Guy Ritchie to direct the remake of 'Hercules'

ANI / Jun 18, 2022, 11:24 (IST)

Guy Ritchie, who directed 'Aladdin' is set to direct the upcoming live-action adaptation of the 1997 classic 'Hercules.' Ritchie's most recent project with Jake Gyllenhaal was an untitled action thriller. 'Operation Fortune: Ruse de guerre,' which was planned to be released in the first few months of 2022 but has since been pushed back without an official release date, was written and directed by him.

'Avengers: Endgame' directors Joe and Anthony Russo to produce live-action ‘Hercules’ remake

TIMESOFINDIA.COM / May 01, 2020, 19:55 (IST)

A year after the phenomenal success of their film ‘Avengers: Endgame’, the Russo brother – Joe and Anthony, are getting ready to roll out their next action-adventure of epic proportions.

Rachel Bilson is up for 'The O C' reunion

PTI / Jun 24, 2017, 11:39 (IST)

Actress Rachel Bilson is open to a revival of teen drama television series 'The O C' but is unsure what the show would be like now.
